headline: Environmental and Facilities Services Stocks Q4 Teardown: Rollins (NYSE:ROL) Vs The Rest
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at environmental and facilities services stocks, starting with Rollins (NYSE:ROL).
